      "description": "Looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver! While it definitely shows some honest cosmetic wear and signs of use from its years on the road, it still runs well and is ready for its next chapter. It's a great opportunity to get a functional, sturdy car at a very accessible price point!",
