    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of swirls or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the premium leather is supple and unmarked, the carpets are pristine, and the interior still carries that signature new-car aroma. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and exceptionally low mileage. It has never seen inclement weather or a commercial car wash, having been hand-detailed exclusively. If you are seeking a turn-key, investment-grade example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered, this is your opportunity.",
